Text.string: Yooo! Let's do something RIGHTEOUS!
S'up? Name's Chadd, that's with a double-D. Like, for “double danger”. You wanna go on an extreme adventure? Gonna be extreme, brah! Trust a Chadd, you don't wanna miss this!
They look super angry, haha! Perfect! Don't want to have to go easy on 'em, ya know?
Sick air, brah! Way to stick the landing!
Wicked jump! Parkour!
Mega jump! Dig your style, brah!
Woo! Hardcore parkour!
Catch some air! Yeah!
Now let's go find us some saurians to punch!
One sec, I'm gonna try some martial arts I learned from this super-wise jabber.||—Nope!
Wait! I got this!
I don't got this!
Ugh... I'm all right...
Super all right...
Just gotta... walk it off...
Friggin'... nailed it...
Just a few... claw wounds... and bites...
I've seen worse but not by much. You need meds.
I wouldn't go another round, love.
You have sustained mortal injuries, human.
That ain't bare-knuckle! That was a love-fest.
Did you see that? Hohh, mega-extreme!

Minor internal bleeding, few broken ribs, whatevaaa! When you taste the danger, you're gonna taste blood! 'Cause that's what danger tastes like, brah! Ooh, ooh! I got a new idea for another. Epic. STUNT!
Woo! Taste the danger! Follow Chadd!
Uhh, your last “stunt” almost got you killed.
Are we entirely sure that's a good idea?
That seems... inadvisable.
You look like you got turned inside out.
Listen, brah. When danger calls, you answer, brah. You answer!
Hello, danger. It's me. Moze.
[sigh] Yes. Acha, hello.
I am answering this fictional call.
Hey, danger! Let's get this show on the road!
Wooo! Good answer, brah!
Chadd wants you to witness this badass BASE jump! Get ready for it!
Aren't you gonna get, like, a parachute or something?
Uh, doesn't basejumping usually involve a parachute?
I would advise you to use a parachute.
I mean, even I'd use a parachute, but hey, it's your life. Or death, as it were.
Pffft. Whaaat?! Parachutes are like, the diapers of the sky, man. They're for babies! Don't you wanna live on the edge?! On the edge of danger?!
Just let me know when you're ready for this, brah!
Just fire your gun and I'll jump! It'll be like, my starting pistol, y'know? Whoo! Chadd!
Waooooo!
I've been super into bare-knuckle boxing lately. Fought my little brah Bradd, jabber, a tree, you name it. But today, I'm feeling super extreme. I'm thinkin' mano a sauro. I'm talkin' SAURIAN BOXING!
I live to TASTE THE DANGERRRRR!
Ughh... righteous...
Ugh, I'm all right...
Ugh, that was... extreme...
Extreme... h-hemorrhaging...
Just, uh... catchin' my breath...
I'm good...
Woooo! Hell to the hell yeah! Oh my hemorrhaging viscera, that was freakin' raaaaaaaaad!

All right, all right all right all right—new stunt! What goes down, must go up! That's how that saying goes in DANGER TOWN! This elevator over here? It's way too slow! Let's speed it up with some friggin' ROCKET BOOSTERS!
Rockets. On an... elevator.
Aaaand you're sure about this?
This seems most unwise.
Well, you live how you wanna live! And die the same way, I suppose.
What I heard was, “Hell yeah! Rocket time!” Go get some! This is gonna be like a stuntgasm, brah!
Those'll do! STRAP 'EM ON! IT'S DANGER TIME!
One more!
I really think that's enough.
Wait, you're going to—ngh, really?
This is entirely excessive.
I mean... if you're sure.
Now, the big saurians eat those little grog dudes like slimy popcorn. So I'm gonna lather myself up with their guts! Woo! Grog hunt! Let's go!
Don't be a wuss! One more!
Righteous! Now back off! I'm gonna be the first to ride this bad boy.||—You ready for this, Boosty Jammer?! That's the elevator's name now.
Great.
Okay.
That is a terrible name.
Hahaha! I love this guy.
Waooo! Now SET IT OFF! Shoot the ignition! Shoot iiiiiiit!
One way ticket to Stuntopia!
Stunterinoville!
Time for a stunticle! Wait, not that one, it sounds gross, uh.
This is gonna be stuntubular!
Stunt-halla!
Taste the dangerrrrrrrrr!
That man died as he lived. It's... almost enviable.
You know, you've gotta admire his spirit.
I will never understand what compelled that man.
Hghh, I'm gonna miss that mad feckin' idjit.
Extreme!
Righteous!
Follow me!
Ring, ring, brah. Ring, ring. It's for you. Ring. Ring!
Hnnnggg! Get pumped!
Head over there and watch the righteousness!
That's one!
This is gonna be the shit!
Booster time!
Now we're talkin'!
More! MORE!
When this is all over, I want you to have at the RIGHTEOUS LOOT STASH I've got up at my house, okay?
Righteously extreme. Now hand 'em over so I can lather it up, brah!
Weaaak, it didn't go! But nah, it's all good. You just shoot the igniter. That'll do it for sure!
Whew, these things stink! Must've peed themselves. Extreme-ly stinky! Which is perfect!
Whoa, there's one! Guess that grog juice works! Wonder what it tastes like! Whatever! Let's fight!
